We promised something big and something green, and today we’re very excited to announce that we are Australia’s only carbon negative pet food.  
 
Green in name and nature, we’ve been working hard behind the scenes to reduce our carbon footprint across our entire supply chain. From the sourcing of our ingredients to the way in which we prepare and package our recipes, along with our choice of suppliers and delivery courier, we’ve opted for the most sustainable and eco-friendly options where possible.   
 
Our aim will always be carbon negative, but where we cannot reduce, we offset our emissions, and are proud to sponsor some of the best carbon offset projects in Australia, which sees us planting native trees in abundance.  
 
Check out our brand-new Sustainability page below to discover all the ways in which we are supporting a greener future 🍃

https://lyka.com.au/sustainability

​
​#lykaiscarbonnegative #sustainablepetfood #feedgoodfeeling
